title: New PS4 Custom Faceplates Launching in Australia This November
text:
New PS4 Custom Faceplates Launching in Australia This November 
Published By: Gamespot.com - Yesterday 
PlayStation Australia has announced that new coloured custom faceplates for the PlayStation 4 will be launching in Australia on November 19....
